posting_body: ['Bright South Facing One Bedroom at The Chase!', '#221', 'Property Address', '5709 Rowland Rd - 221 | Minnetonka, MN 55343', 'Available: 07/22/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'You will find your home at The Chase in Minnetonka.', 'Take delight in the distinctive finishes and unique floor plan designs.', 'Enjoy underground parking, stainless steel appliances, and relaxing in the rooftop community lounge and SkyDeck.', 'Your new neighborhood is secluded in Minnetonka off Shady Oak Road.', 'South facing and overlooking Rowland Road, apartment #221 is a spacious one-bedroom apartment featuring a walk-thru closet, personal balcony, and corner kitchen.', 'This apartment home includes roller mesh window blinds, light plank flooring, dark upper and lower cabinetry, and granite counter tops.', 'Call our leasing office at', 'show contact info', 'today to schedule a showing.', 'Visit <URL> for more information and availability.', 'Note: Photo(s) in this listing are a representation of the property and may not be the exact photos of this available apartment.', 'Amenities', 'Keyless Entry', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Bike Storage', 'Underground Parking', 'In-Unit Washer/Dryer', 'Smoke-Free Living', '4th Floor Lounge', 'Community SkyDeck', 'Fitness Room', 'Luxury Finishes', 'Storage', 'On-Site Management', 'Online Rent Payments', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 633', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,575.00', 'Available: 07/22/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
